    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i hear u but honestly im just super stressed about the money. if i just clean it with some peroxide, put a thick layer of that honey on, and wrap it tight with a bandage, and it stops bleeding, isn't that basically the same as what a doctor would do for a minor cut? i feel like i can manage this if i'm just careful with it. is there any real reason why honey wouldn't work here?",
